{% comment %}
  Ascend Performance Nutrition
  Sleep MasterClass
  Personalization via URL params: ?tier= ?score= ?name=
{% endcomment %}

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  #apn-mc-sleep * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  #apn-mc-sleep {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #f0f0f0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-container {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-container--wide {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-hero {
    padding: 60px 0 48px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(7,165,195,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #07a5c3;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-ring {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #07a5c3;
    background: rgba(7,165,195,0.06);
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-ring::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(7,165,195,0.2);
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-number {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #07a5c3;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-tier-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mc-tier-badge--rookie    { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15);  color: #22c55e; border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
  .mc-tier-badge--competitor { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: #f59e0b; border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3); }
  .mc-tier-badge--athlete   { background: rgba(7,165,195,0.15);  color: #07a5c3; border: 1px solid rgba(7,165,195,0.3); }
  .mc-tier-badge--elite     { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.15); color: #8b5cf6; border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3); }
  .mc-tier-badge--champion  { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15);  color: #ef4444; border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3); }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-hero-headline {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-hero-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #888;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-meta-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #555;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-meta-row span {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-meta-dot {
    width: 3px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #333;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #141414;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section-label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #07a5c3;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section-intro {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #888;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── STAT CARDS ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stat-card {
    background: #111;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stat-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(7,165,195,0.3);
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stat-number {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #07a5c3;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stat-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── CAUSE CARDS ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-causes-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-card {
    background: #0e0e0e;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-card:hover,
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-card.active {
    border-color: #07a5c3;
    background: rgba(7,165,195,0.05);
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(7,165,195,0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-card.active .mc-cause-body {
    max-height: 200px;
    opacity: 1;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cause-fix {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #07a5c3;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ── PROTOCOL ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-card {
    background: #0e0e0e;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px;
    display: none;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-card.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: #07a5c3;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-items {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-items li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaa;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-week-items li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 7px;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #07a5c3;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-tier-selector {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-tier-btn {
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    background: transparent;
    color: #666;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-tier-btn.active,
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-tier-btn:hover {
    border-color: #07a5c3;
    color: #07a5c3;
    background: rgba(7,165,195,0.08);
  }

  /* ── SCIENCE CALLOUT ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-callout {
    background: rgba(7,165,195,0.06);
    border-left: 3px solid #07a5c3;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-callout-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #07a5c3;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-callout p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #aaa;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── PRODUCT CARDS ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-stack-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-card {
    background: #0e0e0e;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(7,165,195,0.3);
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-name {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-why {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-dose {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #07a5c3;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-price {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: right;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-price span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #555;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ── QUOTE ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-quote {
    padding: 40px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-quote-text {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #ddd;
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-quote-attr {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #444;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── CTA SECTION ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cta-section {
    padding: 60px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cta-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4.5vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-cta-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 340px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 15px 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--primary {
    background: #07a5c3;
    color: #000;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--primary:hover {
    background: #09bbd9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--dark {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--dark:hover {
    border-color: #444;
    background: #222;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: #555;
    border: 1px solid #222;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-btn--ghost:hover {
    color: #888;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-discount-badge {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #07a5c3;
    margin-top: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-discount-badge strong {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-footer {
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #141414;
    text-align: center;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-footer-values {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #333;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-footer-signoff {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── PROGRESS BAR ── */
  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-progress {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: #111;
    z-index: 999;
  }

  #apn-mc-sleep .mc-progress-bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: #07a5c3;
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.1s linear;
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-hero { padding: 48px 0 36px; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-section { padding: 44px 0; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-ring { width: 120px; height: 120px; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-score-number { font-size: 44px; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-product-price { text-align: left; }
    #apn-mc-sleep .mc-meta-row { gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>

<div id="apn-mc-sleep">
  <div class="mc-progress"><div class="mc-progress-bar" id="mcProgressBar"></div></div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="mc-hero">
    <div class="mc-container">
      <div class="mc-eyebrow">Ascend Performance Nutrition</div>
      <div class="mc-score-ring">
        <div class="mc-score-number" id="mcScoreNum">--</div>
        <div class="mc-score-label">Sleep Score</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mc-tier-badge" id="mcTierBadge">Loading...</div>
      <h1 class="mc-hero-headline" id="mcHeadline">Your Sleep Is Limiting Everything Else</h1>
      <p class="mc-hero-sub" id="mcSubline">Deep, restorative sleep is where adaptation happens. Without it, every rep, every meal, every supplement underperforms.</p>
      <div class="mc-meta-row">
        <span>Sleep MasterClass</span>
        <span class="mc-meta-dot"></span>
        <span>6 min read</span>
        <span class="mc-meta-dot"></span>
        <span>7 action items</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT IT'S COSTING YOU -->
  <div class="mc-section">
    <div class="mc-container">
      <div class="mc-section-label">The Cost</div>
      <h2 class="mc-section-title">What a Low Sleep Score Actually Means</h2>
      <p class="mc-section-intro" id="mcCostIntro">Your quiz results point to a real gap. Here is what the research says it is costing you right now.</p>

      <div class="mc-stats-grid">
        <div class="mc-stat-card">
          <div class="mc-stat-number">23%</div>
          <div class="mc-stat-desc">Drop in muscle protein synthesis with less than 7 hours of sleep per night</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc-stat-card">
          <div class="mc-stat-number">11x</div>
          <div class="mc-stat-desc">Higher cortisol reactivity when chronically under-slept, stalling fat loss and recovery</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc-stat-card">
          <div class="mc-stat-number">40%</div>
          <div class="mc-stat-desc">Reduction in next-day decision-making and reaction time after a single bad night</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mc-callout">
        <div class="mc-callout-title">The Mechanism</div>
        <p>During slow-wave sleep (Stage 3), growth hormone is released in its largest pulse of the day. Miss this window and you miss the primary driver of tissue repair, fat oxidation, and strength adaptation. No supplement replaces it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ROOT CAUSES -->
  <div class="mc-section">
    <div class="mc-container">
      <div class="mc-section-label">Diagnosis</div>
      <h2 class="mc-section-title">Which Problem Is Yours?</h2>
      <p class="mc-section-intro">Tap the pattern that matches your experience. Each has a different fix.</p>

      <div class="mc-causes-grid">
        <div class="mc-cause-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
          <div class="mc-cause-icon">🌀</div>
          <div>
            <div class="mc-cause-title">Can't Fall Asleep</div>
            <div class="mc-cause-body">
              Cortisol and adrenaline are still elevated at bedtime. Common triggers: late training, blue light past 9pm, unresolved stress, or caffeine too close to bed.
              <span class="mc-cause-fix">Fix: Cortisol wind-down protocol + magnesium glycinate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc-cause-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
          <div class="mc-cause-icon">⏰</div>
          <div>
            <div class="mc-cause-title">Wake Up in the Middle of the Night</div>
            <div class="mc-cause-body">
              Blood sugar crashes, cortisol spikes at 2-3am, or sympathetic nervous system activation from unprocessed stress. The liver runs out of stored glycogen and your body wakes you to fuel the brain.
              <span class="mc-cause-fix">Fix: Strategic carb timing before bed + ashwagandha</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc-cause-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
          <div class="mc-cause-icon">😴</div>
          <div>
            <div class="mc-cause-title">Sleep 8 Hours but Still Tired</div>
            <div class="mc-cause-body">
              Duration is not the issue. Sleep quality is. Insufficient slow-wave sleep due to magnesium deficiency, alcohol, or high training load without adequate recovery between sessions.
              <span class="mc-cause-fix">Fix: Sleep architecture optimization + Function (Magnesium)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 30-DAY PROTOCOL -->
  <div class="mc-section">
    <div class="mc-container">
      <div class="mc-section-label">The Protocol</div>
      <h2 class="mc-section-title">30 Days to Fix the Gap</h2>
      <p class="mc-section-intro">Personalized to your tier. The principles do not change. The depth does.</p>

      <div class="mc-tier-selector" id="mcTierSelector">
        <button class="mc-tier-btn" data-tier="rookie" onclick="selectTier('rookie')">Rookie</button>
